Master Card List
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Farm and Monster Rancher Cards: Monster Rancher CCG (Artbox, 2000): Card Lists: Master Card List
By Lisa Shock on Tuesday, February 12, 2008 - 09:04 am:

  • A total of 138 unique cards were released!
  • There are 99 regular cards.
  • Each rare card was also produced as a foil card.
  • There were 6 promotional cards packed in magazines in 2000.
  • All regular cards have a silver imprint saying "first edition".
  • The promo cards packed in magazines do not have the first edition stamp.
  • 100 sets of framed promo cards, with the first edition stamp, were given away at Comiccon 1999.
  • These 100 sets are the only known promo cards to have the first edition seal.


Rarity: C stands for Common, U stands for Uncommon, R stands for Rare. M indicates magazine promo cards.
